---
import PageLayout from '../layouts/PageLayout.astro';
---

<PageLayout
  title="Privacy Policy — 1404"
  description="How 1404 LLC handles customer data, personal information, and third-party integrations."
>
  <section class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 pt-40 pb-24">
    <h1 class="font-display text-4xl md:text-5xl text-text-primary mb-4">Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="text-text-muted text-sm mb-12">Last updated: April 9, 2026</p>

    <div class="prose prose-invert max-w-none space-y-8 text-text-secondary">

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl text-text-primary font-display mb-3">Who we are</h2>
        <p>
          1404 LLC ("1404", "we", "us") operates Mission Control, an AI assistant platform
          for owner-operated construction and manufacturing companies. Contact:
          <a href="mailto:holden@1404.io" class="text-copper hover:underline">holden@1404.io</a>
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl text-text-primary font-display mb-3">What we collect</h2>
        <p>We collect only what's needed to operate the service:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-1">
          <li><strong>Account info</strong>: name, email address, phone (optional, for MFA), role.</li>
          <li><strong>Authentication data</strong>: password hashes, MFA secrets, session cookies, device trust tokens.</li>
          <li><strong>Business data you provide</strong>: files you upload, messages you send the AI assistant, knowledge base content.</li>
          <li><strong>Integration data</strong>: when you connect QuickBooks Online, Microsoft 365, or Google Workspace, we receive OAuth tokens and access the scopes you grant during consent.</li>
          <li><strong>Operational logs</strong>: request timestamps, error reports, usage telemetry (anonymized).</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl text-text-primary font-display mb-3">How we use it</h2>
        <p>
          Your data is used exclusively to provide and improve Mission Control for your
          organization. We do not sell data, share it with advertisers, or use it to
          train third-party AI models. AI processing happens through Anthropic's Claude
          API under a commercial data-use agreement that prohibits training on your content.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl text-text-primary font-display mb-3">Third-party integrations</h2>
        <p>
          When you connect an integration, we store OAuth tokens in AWS Secrets Manager
          (encrypted with per-client KMS keys). We request only the minimum scopes needed.
        </p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-1">
          <li><strong>QuickBooks Online</strong>: accounting scope — reads P&amp;L, balance sheet, cash flow, AR/AP, invoices, bills, customers, vendors. Write access is gated on per-call approval.</li>
          <li><strong>Microsoft 365</strong>: email, calendar, OneDrive, SharePoint, Teams (read); Mail.Send (send-as-user with explicit confirmation).</li>
          <li><strong>Google Workspace</strong>: Gmail, Calendar, Drive — same pattern as M365.</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl text-text-primary font-display mb-3">Where it lives</h2>
        <p>
          All data is hosted on AWS infrastructure in the United States (us-east-1).
          Databases are encrypted at rest with AWS KMS. Transport is TLS 1.2+.
          Each client tenant is isolated on its own EC2 instance with its own
          KMS key, S3 bucket, and IAM role.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl text-text-primary font-display mb-3">How long we keep it</h2>
        <p>
          Business data is retained as long as your subscription is active. On termination,
          we provide a 30-day export window, then permanently delete all customer data and
          revoke all OAuth tokens within 60 days. Activity logs are retained for 12 months
          for compliance and debugging.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl text-text-primary font-display mb-3">Your rights</h2>
        <p>
          You can request access, correction, export, or deletion of your data at any time
          by emailing <a href="mailto:holden@1404.io" class="text-copper hover:underline">holden@1404.io</a>.
          We respond within 7 business days.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl text-text-primary font-display mb-3">Changes</h2>
        <p>
          If we materially change this policy, we'll notify account owners via email at
          least 14 days before the change takes effect.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl text-text-primary font-display mb-3">Contact</h2>
        <p>
          Questions, concerns, or data requests:
          <a href="mailto:holden@1404.io" class="text-copper hover:underline">holden@1404.io</a>
          <br />1404 LLC, Ann Arbor, MI
        </p>
      </section>

    </div>
  </section>
</PageLayout>
